comment: Lillard (POR) makes contact with Westbrook (OKC) that affects his RSBQ as he attempts to split the double team.
Plumlee (POR) obtains a legal guarding position prior to absorbing the contact from Westbrook (OKC).
Plumlee (POR) sets the screen on Roberson (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Plumlee (POR) cleanly blocks Ibaka's (OKC) layup attempt.
Roberson (OKC) makes contact with Crabbe's (POR) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Westbrook (OKC) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
